OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudier
OL,6,Finto the evening, with heavy showers
OL,7,Fskirting the far southeast, perhaps
OL,8,Fgiving the odd rumble of thunder here.
OL,9,FWhile mainly cloudy, becoming
OL,10,Fgenerally dry later in the night.
OL,11,FMostly mild, but chilly in western
OL,12,Frural areas.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FBrightest early on, with
OL,15,Fsome warm sunny spells, although cloud
OL,16,Famounts increasing from the south, in
OL,17,Fadvance of heavier and more prolonged
OL,18,Frain spreading in later, perhaps
OL,19,Feventually thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
